{"item_id":"051b850fbf:0","text":"PxrRampLightFilter 使用 ramp 来控制灯光。它也可用于以人工和艺术化方式控制灯光衰减。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:1","text":"Parameters（参数）"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:2","text":"Ramp Direction"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:3","text":"Ramp Type"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:4","text":"指定 ramp 应用的方向。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:5","text":"distToLight(0) - 到灯光的距离。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:6","text":"linear(1) - 线性 ramp。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:7","text":"spherical(2) - 球形 ramp。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:8","text":"radial(3) - 径向 ramp。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:9","text":"Begin Distance"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:10","text":"ramp 开始的位置距离。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:11","text":"End Distance"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:12","text":"ramp 结束的位置距离。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:13","text":"Ramp"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:14","text":"Ramp"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:15","text":"定义 knot 数量。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:16","text":"Ramp Knots"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:17","text":"knot 值数组。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:18","text":"Ramp Floats"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:19","text":"float 值数组。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:20","text":"Ramp Interpolation"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:21","text":"ramp 插值的 Type（类型）："}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:22","text":"linear"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:23","text":"catmull-rom"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:24","text":"bspline"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:25","text":"constant"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:26","text":"Multiplier"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:27","text":"Density"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:28","text":"控制投射效果的强度。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:29","text":"Invert"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:30","text":"指定应用前是否反转投射纹理。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:31","text":"Intensity"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:32","text":"下方 diffuse 和 specular 贡献的全局 Multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:33","text":"Diffuse"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:34","text":"此 light filter 结果用于 diffuse contribution 的 multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:35","text":"Specular"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:36","text":"此 light filter 结果用于 specular contribution 的 multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:37","text":"Color Ramp"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:38","text":"Color Ramp"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:39","text":"定义 knot 数量。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:40","text":"Color Ramp Knots"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:41","text":"knot 值数组。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:42","text":"Ramp Colors"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:43","text":"color 值数组。"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:44","text":"Color Ramp Interpolation"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:45","text":"color ramp 插值的 Type（类型）："}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:46","text":"linear"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:47","text":"catmull-rom"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:48","text":"bspline"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:49","text":"constant"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:50","text":"Combine Mode"}
{"item_id":"051b850fbf:51","text":"PxrRampLightFilter 的 combine mode 始终为相乘。"}
